{"name":"Loyal to the End","type":"divineGift","img":"icons/magic/holy/angel-winged-humanoid-blue.webp","data":{"word":"Martyrdom","description":"Commit Effort. A visible NPC immediately becomes cooperative and reverent toward you, doing for you all they would do for someone of great importance in their culture or faith. Worthy foes get a Spirit save to resist this effect. If you do something that improves life for the NPC in some way, such as reclaiming something stolen from them or saving someone they hold dear, they remain cooperative even after the Effort is reclaimed and join your cult or religion (as defined by the Apotheosis Word) if able.","constant":false,"instant":false,"onTurn":false,"action":true,"smite":false,"noEffort":false,"atWill":true,"scene":false,"day":false,"greater":false,"combatPower":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"9kLb9OnQ3UEYBEz7":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.FAcXzhVsym3YeIjn"}},"_id":"0u33Vpowk5H1Guqa"}
