{"name":"Martyr's Retaliation","type":"divineGift","img":"icons/magic/holy/angel-winged-humanoid-blue.webp","data":{"word":"Martyrdom","description":"You may Commit Effort for the scene when you take damage. The creature that damaged you takes @RollDmg[leveld10] emotional damage, or @RollDmg[leveld10] from your followers attacking them if you have a Small Mob or more present that are loyal to you and able to attack the offending assailant. Worthy foes may make a Spirit saving throw to halve this damage if it is emotional damage, or an Evasion saving throw to halve this damage if it comes from your followers.","constant":false,"instant":true,"onTurn":false,"action":false,"smite":true,"noEffort":false,"atWill":false,"scene":true,"day":false,"greater":true,"combatPower":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"9kLb9OnQ3UEYBEz7":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.AYz4zzLMSYVRwqum"}},"_id":"TMi4EEhaav7NulCL"}
{"name":"Rebuke the Sinner","type":"divineGift","img":"icons/magic/holy/angel-winged-humanoid-blue.webp","data":{"word":"Martyrdom","description":"You may Commit Effort for the scene when a creature has just Committed Effort for any reason. The Effort is lost, and the creature must Commit it again as an Instant action if their desired effect is to come to pass. If they do, they can no longer use the associated gift or other power for the rest of the scene. This gift can only be used once per scene on a given target.","constant":false,"instant":true,"onTurn":false,"action":false,"smite":false,"noEffort":false,"atWill":false,"scene":true,"day":false,"greater":true,"combatPower":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"9kLb9OnQ3UEYBEz7":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.BfTBU8Zyerr3CPRx"}},"_id":"VwuDAkzVbb0vCNK4"}
