{"name":"Salve the Soul","type":"divineGift","img":"icons/magic/holy/angel-winged-humanoid-blue.webp","data":{"word":"Martyrdom","description":"You can reduce or quell a particular negative emotion in the target of your choosing, such as despair, grief, anger, or hate. If you do so, you automatically learn the source of the emotion and the subject of it, and what the target knows about that subject. The target will no longer feel that emotion towards the original subject until you release them from the effect. Lesser foes are automatically affected, while worthy foes can save versus Spirit to resist the effect.","constant":false,"instant":false,"onTurn":false,"action":true,"smite":false,"noEffort":true,"atWill":false,"scene":false,"day":false,"greater":false,"combatPower":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"9kLb9OnQ3UEYBEz7":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ApIO4NXLRtgeUjGw"}},"_id":"s7jNMWwq0EZ7hrMq"}
